    <item>
      <title>Carols at the Pond</title>
      <link>https://www.ouroakley.uk/events/odpc/2025/12/20/carols-at-the-pond/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.ouroakley.uk/events/odpc/2025/12/20/carols-at-the-pond/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Much-loved village carol singing with the community, attended by the Mayor of Basingstoke and Deane. Taking place at Village Pond, East Oakley.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Donations support local groups and organisations.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Join us for this cherished annual tradition as we gather around the village pond for festive carol singing. A wonderful community event that brings everyone together to celebrate the Christmas season.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
